# The Revelation Riddle  
### Revealing a Hidden Prophetic Architecture in Scripture

Welcome to the online edition of **The Revelation Riddle**, a study built entirely on, and grounded in, the King James Bible and the biblical method of typology (Gal. 4:24; 1 Cor. 10:6,11).

Use the table of contents below to read each chapter.

